<h2>Eiffel Tower, Paris, France</h2>
<p> A symbol of Paris and one of the most beloved landmarks globally, the Eiffel Tower offers panoramic views and a dazzling light show every hour at night, making it a must-visit attraction in Europe 
.</p>

<h2>Taj Mahal, Agra: </h2>
<p>A white marble mausoleum built by Mughal Emperor Shah Jahan in memory of his wife Mumtaz Mahal, recognized as one of the Seven Wonders of the World and a UNESCO World Heritage Site 
.</p>